	too many things are made PARTIAL right now so that unification works

========================================================================================
formatter.sig.sml 
formatter.sml

	These 2 files represent the ForML pretty-printer found in /afs/cs/user/er/pub/.
Minor modifications were made so that it compiles with SML/NJ 1.09 and so that
it can handle bailouts with an indication of the nesting.
These changes are documented at the beginning of formatter.sml.

========================================================================================
util.sig.sml
util.sml

	Miscellaneous helper and debugging functions are placed here.

========================================================================================
il.sig.sml
il.sml

	Contains the datatype for the IL.

========================================================================================
ppil.sig.sml
ppil.sml

	Pretty-printing routines for IL datatypes.

========================================================================================
ilutil.sig.sml
ilutil.sml

   Contains helper functions like equality, gensyms, setting type variables, conversions among 
(symbols, varaibles, labels), special labels(it,mk,km,case), path2(mod,con,exp),
(ifthenelse , let, and lambda) makers, basic derived types, basic derived expressions,
type (variable, application) substution, occurs_check.

========================================================================================
ilstatic.sig.sml
ilstatic.sml

  Contains the operational versions of static semantics.

========================================================================================
basis.sig.sml
basis.sml

   Contains the initial basis to compile against.

========================================================================================
infixparse.sig.sml
infixparse.sml

	Performs infix parsing of Ast expressions and Ast patterns.
Note that Asts are obtainable from the SML/NJ visible compiler.

========================================================================================
pat.sig.sml
pat.sml
	
	Pattern compiler.

========================================================================================
toil.sig.sml
toil.sml

	Actual translation that takes AST to IL.

========================================================================================

	